<p>We also have momentary errors where a web site is down.</p>

<p>Also cases were OP then comments or edits saying the problem has disappeared.</p>

<p>Cases where an install has failed and shows the logs - SO has a close reason for just "Programming, but not Code dumps." do we need something similar</p>

